{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "擅闖者", "storyInfo": "高登假意幫助費爾南，差遣她去萊茵生態園，實則打算藉機把她和娜斯提等人一併扣押。但他趕到時，只看見生態園的植物盡數枯萎。另一邊，從生態園偷走了骨筆的費爾南逃回住處，卻發現女妖客人不翼而飛。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g12_trimountrestarea", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，這就是萊茵生命最年輕的主任，克麗斯騰女士曾經的左膀右臂，生態園和園區工程部的雙料負責人——娜斯提主任嗎？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……梅希亞，這就是你說的“後續事宜”？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，是的。解說員可以幫工程部提高溝通效率，也能加大對萊茵生態園的宣傳力度，避免萊茵再次受到預展時的冷遇。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提主任，我聽說園區上空飄浮的種植單元並未裝配螺旋槳，而是利用咒言產生升力？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不完全是，不以聲音為媒介的咒言需要與機械結合才能維持動力。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，骨筆對於您來說一定十分重要。如果遺失會造成嚴重的後果嗎？比如喪失記憶或者生病？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "骨筆於我只是工具，不會對……生理造成影響。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那平時您在工作之餘是怎麼緩解壓力、恢復精神的呢？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1", "posfrom": "250,0", "posto": "120,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全套的羽角護理會讓您放鬆一點嗎？您推薦哪個品牌的護理套裝？啊，我可以摸一下您的角，來判斷產品效果——", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-30,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解說員小姐，你的問題已經與我們的工作無關了。我會讓研究員帶你參觀生態園，他們可以解答你的疑惑。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是——", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些事情，我想要向梅希亞小姐單獨確認。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g10_ecolab", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登又想做什麼？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您何出此言？長官知道萊茵現在的處境難免會讓一些同行得寸進尺，要是影響到檢修工作，得不償失。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只是出於好心。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直以為他身上那套昂貴的西裝就是用良知換來的。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#17$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#17$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "況且，我很難想像一名特聘解說員的詢問會如此文不對題，除非，從一開始她就另有目的。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你必須維護自己的上司，所以我不會對此加以指責，但你也知道，在我面前你可以說實話。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我確實覺得這件事不太對勁，但我認為高登長官絕不是在針對您。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "理由？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提主任，我們才達成協議不久，沒有道理在這麼短的時間內向您二次施壓。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果長官真的另有所圖，以他的謹慎，一定會把計劃原委詳盡地告訴我，避免出任何問題。除非……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除非他藏著秘密。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每天總有一些時段，他會從辦公區域消失，一開始我以為他只是去跟客戶談投資。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾天前一名投資人與我寒暄的時候，誇讚長官只用一次談判就完成了所有合約。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我記得長官說過，他與這名投資人的談判很不順利，需要安排更多時間……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，娜斯提主任，您幹嘛這樣看著我？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你違反了秘書的第一條準則。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且你在梳理線索的時候，沒有之前那麼緊繃。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是嗎？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "依照準則，我應該關上耳朵，閉緊嘴巴，只為長官著想，但現在我也不知道他到底在想什麼了。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是在聊我嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "！", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#12$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很高興看到你們相處得如此融洽，我還以為小梅這樣不善言詞的孩子，除了工作，不會交到朋友。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登長官，我……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這條規則也在她的秘書準則裡？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，娜斯提主任，你真會開玩笑。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願你不是來聽笑話的，我不擅長。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是來向你致歉的。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又要兼顧參展計劃，又要檢查上萬件展品，實在是勞心費神。希望我也能盡一些綿薄之力。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你派來的那位解說員很“專業”。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "見到自己崇拜的對象難免會有些緊張。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒不知道自己還有這樣一名“粉絲”。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#5$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜她只是太過害羞，又或者——", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是為了故意避嫌。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這是什麼意思？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#6$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小梅，把解說員小姐請過來，我有幾個關於娜斯提主任的問題想問她。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1", "posfrom": "-300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，她不見了……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼——", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.92, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#11$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2049_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提主任！所有植物的養分供應都被切斷了，但主控程式並沒有報錯，中控電腦的硬體也沒有出現任何損壞跡象，就好像……", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2049_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "控制它們的指令全被取消了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。為實驗植物提供養分的能源轉換器正在逆向運轉，如果不能儘快修復指令，這些植物再過幾分鐘就會死亡——", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2049_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，枯萎已經開始了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"image": "38_g10_ecolab", "duration": 4.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$act15_intro", "key": "$act15_loop", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g13_ecolabwithered", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"image": "68_g13_ecolabwithered", "duration": 3.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_plantwither", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先是一片葉子，而後是一根枝條、一棵植株……濃密的綠意在短短幾秒鐘內，被從整面生態實驗牆上無情地剝去。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們停下了腳步，呆呆地看著眼前瞬間發生的災難。所有人都知道那些蜷縮的、如枯骨一般的枝葉代表著什麼。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走向絕境的，不只是這些樹。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還愣著幹嘛！優先移植展覽要用的實驗品，那是我們僅剩的一批幼苗了——", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都停下來！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#5$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……", "name": "研究員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_530_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從現在開始，園區警衛隊將接手萊茵對生態園的管轄權，進行全方位的事故調查，在取證完成之前所有人都不准靠近設備！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "警衛隊。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "duration": 0.3, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在。", "name": "園區警衛隊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封鎖生態園。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "園區警衛隊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_901_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，娜斯提主任，我為你們夭折的實驗成果感到痛心，但為園區的安全考慮，我必須做這個決定。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到事故調查結果出來之前，你的研究員需要全部撤出實驗室，檢修工作我也會派別人處理。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#4$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些警衛什麼時候等在門外的？警報響起之前，還是之後？", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道你在說什麼。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會讓研究員離開，但我不會走。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高登，你來得太巧了。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "68_g14_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……呼……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們……沒追上來……太好了……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，高登長官，本來應該等您來生態園找我們會合的，但我食言了。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想，我已經找到能幫助那位女妖客人的東西了……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "費爾南攤開緊握的右手，一支通體白色的物體被她托在手心。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "十分鐘前，她在生態園一邊參觀，一邊琢磨究竟什麼能幫助一名年邁的女妖恢復神智。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她知道，那必須是一件對女妖而言非常重要的東西，能喚起本能的東西。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "如命運一般，這根插在樹上的小東西闖入了費爾南的視線。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "晦澀的符號遍布瑩白的“短枝”，四周飄浮的紋路如泛著微光的心電圖波形，透露出不可抗拒的吸引力。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "費爾南見過類似的符號和紋路——這是一支屬於女妖的骨筆。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，娜斯提主任，暫且借用一下您的骨筆，等我的客人恢復健康，我就馬上把它還回去。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#2$1", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，我親愛的客人，整天悶在房間裡真的委屈您啦，我想我找到讓您找回記憶的方法了——", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……客人？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "房間裡空無一人，只有床單上的皺褶證明曾有人來過。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風從大開的窗戶吹進房間，窗台上，一枚黑色的羽角殘片微微晃動。"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她……不見了……", "name": "費爾南"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}